  <section class="section limitations" data-tab="underhood">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header-editorial">
        <div>
          <div class="kicker">What this report is not</div>
          <h2>Limitations &amp; honest caveats</h2>
          <p class="caption" style="margin-top: 12px; max-width: 720px;">
            The divergence score is a ranking signal, not a forecasting model. Three directions where the numbers deserve scepticism before they drive an investment decision.
          </p>
